                        <interp inst="t18590815-name-13" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE THOMAS</persName>
                  </hi>. I was on board the steam-boat on 1st August—there was a shove—I turned to see who pushed against me, and I saw the prisoner with this watch in his hand, which was clenched, and the handle of the watch was peeping out, and in the other hand he had the ring of a guard—he pushed against me, and I was close to the prosecutor—I collared the prisoner, and said, "You rascal, I have got you"—I saw him with the watch in his hand, and heard the ring snap from it—I seized him directly—he dropped the watch—I picked it up, and gave him and the watch to the constable—this is it.</p>
